Chuck Taylor All Star High GS 'Valentine's Day - White'
results.story: Dropping as part of the brand’s Valentine’s Day collection, the Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High GS ‘White’ carries a traditional canvas upper festooned with unique details in honor of February 14. They include heart-printed laces, an embroidered heart on the lateral side and a ‘Made With Love’ graphic on the opposite side. Underfoot, the white rubber outsole features a traditional diamond traction pattern and an all-over print made up of additional red hearts.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star High GS 'Coated Glitter'
Chuck Taylor All Star High GS 'Explore Nature - Allover Koala Print'
results.story: Designed for big kids, the Converse Explore Nature Chuck Taylor All Star GS ‘Allover Koala Print’ enlivens the pink canvas upper with playful graphics depicting the tree-dwelling marsupial. The high-top is appointed with standard Chuck Taylor details, including chrome eyelets, a rubber toe cap and an All Star ankle patch on the medial side. A softened textile lining provides a comfortable fit, while a SmartFOAM sockliner delivers lightweight cushioning with each step.

results.name: Tiempo Legend 8 Club TF PS 'Black Light Photo Blue'
results.story: An artificial-turf soccer shoe built for little kids, the Nike Tiempo Legend 8 Club TF PS ‘Black Light Photo Blue’ provides enhanced ball control, thanks to a molded diamond texture on the synthetic leather forefoot. Inside the shoe, a neon green finish is applied to the foam sockliner, good for lightweight cushioning with each stride. The rubber outsole is equipped with a multidirectional traction pattern based on player-movement analysis compiled by the Nike Sports Research Lab.

results.name: Phantom GT Academy MG GS 'Black Cyber'
Tiempo Legend 8 Club IC GS 'Black Light Photo Blue'
results.story: The Nike Tiempo Legend 8 Club IC GS ‘Black Light Photo Blue’ showcases a simple two-tone palette on an indoor soccer shoe made for big kids. Mesh construction on the heel and tongue provides breathable comfort, while the molded diamond texture on the synthetic leather forefoot delivers superior ball control. The low-profile silhouette is supported by a data-informed rubber outsole, featuring a multi-directional traction pattern developed by the Nike Sports Research Lab.

results.name: Tiempo Legend 8 Club MG GS 'Black Light Photo Blue'
Flex Runner GS 'Game Royal'
results.story: Developed for big kids, the Nike Flex Runner GS ‘Game Royal’ pairs a convenient slip-on build with lightweight cushioning. The streamlined upper is constructed from a blend of stretchy textile and breathable mesh. Structural support is provided by a synthetic leather midfoot cage, featuring elastic straps that wrap over the tongue and around the heel. The sneaker is mounted on a plush foam sole unit that uses flex grooves to accommodate the natural motion of the foot.

results.name: D.O.N. Issue #2 J 'Clear Mint'
results.story: Built for big kids, the adidas D.O.N. Issue #2 J ‘Clear Mint’ updates Donovan Mitchell’s second signature shoe with a vibrant palette designed to stand out on the basketball court. A bright turquoise hue floods the breathable mesh upper, secured with an integrated lacing system for midfoot lockdown. Screaming Pink accents land on the sneaker’s branding elements, including Mitchell’s personal logo on the molded heel overlay. Lightweight cushioning comes courtesy of a podular Bounce midsole.
